# BB Schedule — build after changes

When you finish edits to `main.py`, `requirements.txt`, `build.bat`, or `watch-build.ps1`, run a release build from the project root:

```bat
build.bat
```

This produces `dist\BBSchedule.exe` (build uses `%TEMP%` then copies into `dist` to avoid Google Drive file locks).

For continuous rebuilds while developing, the maintainer can run:

```powershell
.\watch-build.ps1
```

Do not skip the build when the user expects an updated `.exe` after code changes.
